snippet.title: Troy Aikman Nfl Football Trailer 1994
snippet.description:
Troy Aikman Nfl Football Trailer 1994

Official Content From Tradewest

Run Troy's favorite plays and go for the 2 point conversion. You can even build a powerhouse team and go to the Super Bowl with Troy's Team Set-Up. Did they really steal Aikman's brain?
Platforms: Sega Genesis
